subject: HISTORY
text: "The Roman Occupation of Britain has little or no connexion with English History." Discuss this statement.

text: Compare the achievements of the three following sovereigns of England: Alfred, Canute, William I.

text: Illustrate the political influence of the Church between the accession of Henry I and the death of John.

text: Either: Trace the development of the English Parliament up to the death of Edward III. Or: Account for the failure of the first three Edwards to conquer Scotland.
